<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-538-262  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 538 262  OV: 08 538 080.andO; </DOCID><JOURNAL>InfoWorld  June 11 1990 v12 n24 p68(4).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Micrografx Graph Plus version 1.3. (Micrografx Inc.) (SoftwareReview) (one of eight evaluations of presentation software in&quot;Making your point - with style&quot;) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Fridlund, Alan J.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Micrografx Inc's upgraded Graph Plus 1.3 lists at $495 and israted a very good value.andP;  Enhancements to this MS Windows-basedpackage include much improved graphics and data importing andexporting and context-sensitive help.andP;  It is unique in using a'worksheet' rather than a text-entry approach and the MS Windowsgraphical user interface makes it easy to learn and easy to use.andO;Drawing and printing speed are good although some of the otherfunctions are a little slow.andP;  The chart and graph options areexcellent and Graph Plus has the most sophisticated statisticalcalculation abilities of any of the eight packages reviewed.andP;  Thedrawing and editing tools are very good and the clip art librariesare extensive.andP;  The documentation is simply packaged but wellorganized and written, with a good tutorial.andP;  Like manypresentation software packages, Graph Plus does not include aspelling checker.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Micrografx Inc. (products).andO;Product:   Micrografx Graph Plus 1.3 (Presentation software).andO;Topic:     EvaluationPresentation Software.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>